OL,4,Ccleared of coercive control and assault
OL,6,FBargain Hunt auctioneer Charles Hanson
OL,7,Fhas been unanimously cleared at Derby
OL,8,FCrown Court of coercive control and
OL,9,Fassault allegations relating to his
OL,10,Fwife Rebecca Hanson.
OL,12,FCharles Hanson smiled at his parents
OL,13,Fand gave a thumbs-up gesture from the
OL,14,Fdock after the jury foreman returned
OL,15,Fthe not guilty verdicts on charges of
OL,16,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour,
OL,17,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm
OL,18,Fand assault by beating after a three-
OL,19,Fweek trial.
