OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters immediately
OL,7,Foutside the courtroom, Charles Hanson
OL,8,Fsaid: "I'm delighted that after a year
OL,9,Fand a half the truth has finally come
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,F"I can finally live my life again.
OL,14,F"I feel this burden has finally been
OL,15,Flifted.
OL,17,F"It has been a tormentuous time and
OL,18,Fall I want now is to readjust to what
OL,19,Fhas been such an ordeal.
